Package: microsim
Type: Package
Title: A Simulator Package with a collection of basic community models that outputs count data of microbial communities
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Emma Gheysen
Maintainer: Emma Gheysen <emma.gheysen@student.kuleuven.be>
Description: generation of time series and cross-sectional data with support of environmental influence (to be discussed), sample group structure (e.g. time series from different hosts or healthy vs diseased), adjustable external noise level and ideally perturbations
